OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,F"Tell me if you've neglected your
OL,7,Fmum," asked the officer.
OL,9,F"I have," replied David Holyoak.
OL,11,FHolyoak, 54, told police during
OL,12,Finterviews that he could have done
OL,13,Fmore to save his mother Dorothy Morgan.
OL,15,FBoth he and her husband, 61-year-old
OL,16,FRobert Morgan, were convicted of
OL,17,Fmanslaughter of their elderly relative
OL,18,Flast month.
