OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,FToday, at Carlisle Crown Court, Morgan
OL,7,Fwas jailed for three years, the judge
OL,8,Fsaying: "Your negligence was gross and
OL,9,Fserious. You could have done so much
OL,10,Fmore."
OL,12,FHis stepson Holyoak was jailed for two
OL,13,Fyears eight months. The judge told
OL,14,Fhim: "I am in no doubt that you did
OL,15,Flove your mother and did not want her
OL,16,Fto die. However, it is clear that you
OL,17,Fignored the warning signs."
