OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,FCarlisle Crown Court had heard how
OL,7,FDorothy Morgan was found in a
OL,8,Fmalnourished and dehydrated state -
OL,9,Fweighing just four-and-a-half stones -
OL,10,Fwhen she was admitted to the West
OL,11,FCumberland Hospital on 25 January 2021.
OL,13,FShe died in hospital 10 days later.
OL,15,FPolice interviews
OL,17,F"In hindsight, I probably could have
OL,18,Fdone more, but hindsight is 20-20
OL,19,Fvision isn't it?" Robert Morgan told
OL,20,Fofficers during interrogation.
