OL,6,F"Their accounts were that they didn't
OL,7,Fbelieve that Dorothy wanted medical
OL,8,Fintervention, I reject that entirely,"
OL,9,Fsaid Detective Superintendent Matthew
OL,10,FScott.
OL,12,F"We've got clear medical history from
OL,13,FDorothy that when medical intervention
OL,14,Fwas required, Dorothy wanted that
OL,15,Fmedical intervention.
