OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,F"We can see results of blood tests,
OL,7,Fetc, etc, in the past. My own view,
OL,8,Fand it's only my own view, is that
OL,9,Fthey just saw it as a hindrance and
OL,10,Feither couldn't be bothered to get the
OL,11,Fcare for her or just didn't care
OL,12,Fenough to get it."
OL,14,FIt's understood that after retiring
OL,15,FDorothy Morgan became increasingly
OL,16,Fisolated.
OL,18,FHer husband Robert Morgan told the
OL,19,Fcourt that she lost interest in
OL,20,Fgardening and charity work.
