OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,FBut a turning point came on 25 January
OL,7,F2021.
OL,9,FIt was on this date that Robert Morgan
OL,10,Fmade a 999 call.
OL,12,FHe told paramedics he didn't know her
OL,13,Fage or birthday.
OL,15,F"Tell me exactly what's happened," the
OL,16,Femergency call handler asked Morgan.
OL,18,F"The wife has been refusing to get any
OL,19,Fkind of medical help for months," he
OL,20,Fresponded.
