OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,F"She stopped eating, she stopped
OL,7,Fdrinking. She looks like something
OL,8,Ffrom a death camp.
OL,10,F"She can barely sit up now. And I
OL,11,Fcan't go on with this. I'm not
OL,12,Fsupporting behaviour like this
OL,13,Fanymore."
OL,15,FParamedics were deployed to Dorothy
OL,16,FMorgan's home in Whitehaven and she
OL,17,Fwas taken to the West Cumberland
OL,18,FHospital in the town where she died 10
OL,19,Fdays later.
