OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,FShe had early-stage lung cancer, but
OL,7,Fher cause of death was severe
OL,8,Femaciation and infection from
OL,9,Fneglected pressure ulcers.
OL,11,FAfter being found in this condition,
OL,12,Fthe hospital alerted police.
OL,14,FIt was described by a senior
OL,15,Fprosecutor as one of the worst cases
OL,16,Fof manslaughter by gross negligence
OL,17,Fthey've ever seen.
OL,19,FThe 71-year-old was also suffering
OL,20,Ffrom sepsis and hadn't drunk anything
OL,21,Fin more than a week.
