OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,F"This isn't how anybody should should
OL,7,Fdie, simple as that," said Detective
OL,8,FSuperintendent Matthew Scott.
OL,10,F"In pain, in suffering and alone
OL,11,Fessentially. But these cases
OL,12,Fholistically are always shocking.
OL,14,F"I've dealt with very few of these
OL,15,Fcases just because thankfully, they
OL,16,Fare rare. This is like the third case
OL,17,Fof this nature I've dealt with, so
OL,18,Fthere is some reassurance from that, I
OL,19,Fguess.
