OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,F"But cases like this are particularly
OL,7,Fdistressing, especially when we're
OL,8,Ftalking about the elderly in our
OL,9,Fcommunities.
OL,11,F"While Dorothy Morgan met an end full
OL,12,Fof pain and suffering, both men were
OL,13,Fdescribed as completely failing to
OL,14,Fproperly take care of her.
OL,16,F"And it was this failure that killed
OL,17,Ftheir wife and mother."
