OL,3,CHow two men let their 71-year-old wife
OL,4,Cand mother die in her own home
OL,6,FA domestic homicide review is now
OL,7,Fbeing carried out to identify any
OL,8,Flessons to be learnt and if anything
OL,9,Fcould have been done differently to
OL,10,Fprotect Dorothy Morgan.
OL,12,FThis typically happens when an adult's
OL,13,Fdeath happens as a result of violence,
OL,14,Fabuse or neglect by a relative,
OL,15,Fpartner or member of the same
OL,16,Fhousehold.
OL,18,FThis is not connected to the legal
OL,19,Fprocess, but it aims to prevent
OL,20,Fanything like this from happening
OL,21,Fagain.
